text.section: The fees as established by administrative regulation shall be paid to the board, and shall not be refunded in whole or in part.

law.history: Repealed and reenacted 2014 Ky. Acts ch. 90, sec. 5, effective July 15, 2014. -- Amended 1994 Ky. Acts ch. 291, sec. 5, effective July 15, 1994. -- Amended 1988 Ky. Acts ch. 296, sec. 1, effective July 15, 1988. -- Amended 1982 Ky. Acts ch. 64, sec. 2, effective July 15, 1982. -- Created 1972 Ky. Acts ch. 287, sec. 6.
